 * Create virtualenv
 * apt-get install libxml2-dev libxslt-dev libmysqlclient-dev
 * pip install sqlalchemy
 * pip install MySQL-python
 * git clone https://github.com/openstack/python-keystoneclient.git && cd python-keystoneclient  && python setup.py install
 * git clone https://github.com/openstack/python-novaclient.git  && cd python-novaclient && python setup.py install
 * Install beatbox from git  : https://github.com/superfell/Beatbox 
 * Loop through each library sub folder and python setup.py install   

